rkey's first-ever shooting sport medal.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9982732656788674, \"rank\": 0.001686063096515201, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"travelling toParisbut\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"his teammate\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"Sevval Ilayda Tarhan\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics During the event, spectators could not help but notice that Dikec stood out from the rest of his competitors with his minimalist equipment.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"his competitors\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"his minimalist equipment\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, pistol shooters compete wearing specialist eyewear to help improve accuracy and huge protectors in order to block out any distractions.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pistol shooters\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"specialist eyewear\", \"fr